Ok so theres  this guy zack that by totally accident i fell madly in love with. theres nothing i seem to want more then to talk to him be with him and just make him mine. he's coming to stay with me for 4 days on the 19th. im taking him to a concert, throwing him a party, and its going to be the most magically awesome time. theres no one i have ever felt like this for. he makes me feel soo comfortable and makes me feel like im the best thing ever. me and him will make the cutest ever. and the fact that he has a girlfriend kills me but when i talk to him he makes me feel so wanted. and last night he made me a picture that said " i love my ally"... i told him that i loved him and he was deff ok with it. and theres nothing that i want more then him... i can't wait till he's here the things we are going to do and the time that we will spend together is going to be wonderful.... i can't wait til he is mine. :-] 

we will make everyone jealous for being so cute. and perfect. 




&hearts;
